{"tid":902793,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Gundam Battle Operation 2 [15] 留起啲幣煲醋","createTime":"2018-11-15T05:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T05:10:01.000Z","uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19c49dc2c4bfcd4436cbe2149a50cf2a234bac81","tid":902793,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/89/17e7a37039a9731c2b4e9ba4bb10cbp5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F89%2F17e7a37039a9731c2b4e9ba4bb10cbp5.JPG&h=d7e985a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/01/130136_6111afb38475974e54ee07feef29b73f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F01%2F130136_6111afb38475974e54ee07feef29b73f.png&h=b68257b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/311645531/original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F311645531%2Foriginal.gif&h=10f9936e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp&d=5AQysucJKw%2B06WvvYsRLX2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c0fa4b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp</a><br />\n中文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp%2Fhk%2F&d=5AQysucJKw%2B06WvvYsRLX2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=95690f6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/</a><br />\n遊戲Wiki: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2&d=5AQysucJKw%2B06WvvYsRLX2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=83deecdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEKMn0X1MHk&d=5AQysucJKw%2B06WvvYsRLX2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=91e5ae0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><ins>FAQ</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點解我成日斷線</strong><br />\nA. 為己為人, <del>自殺</del> 對戰請用Lan 線<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 間中會遇到隱形敵人/無敵/黑畫面, 係咪有外掛?</strong><br />\nA. <del>掛你老母</del> 有咁嘅情況其實係Lag 機引致, 官方已經公佈咗短期內會有update 去解決問題 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好似已經fix咗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 今集有無EN限制?係咪好似上集兩個鐘先回1粒EN?</strong><br />\nA. 今集廢除咗EN, 玩真人體力制, 燃燒自己嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 有無分Server? 用港定日psn 好?</strong><br />\nA. 今集係國際Server, 港日psn 都係一齊玩, 但之前GBON轉Server 前科, 所以用日psn應該會安全啲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點解無得同朋友一齊開房玩</strong><br />\nA. 除咗Ranking mode之外, 其他2個mode 都可以邀朋友<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣用支援炮擊</strong><br />\nA. 佔點之後會見到有個數字倒數, 當倒數到0之後就可以落機call 炮擊, 威力極大如善用可以一擊逆轉戰況<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 機/武/Parts 點樣升lv?</strong><br />\nA. 用DP直接買下一lv, 如果未有得買即係未夠軍階<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣放炸彈</strong><br />\nA. 1. 基礎戰先有得放<br />\n     2. 去到基地搵 [ ! ]個ICON<br />\n     3. 行到正確嘅位置,就會有話框叫你長按O 裝炸彈<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣出滾地 (緊急迴避)</strong><br />\nA. 如果你部機有&quot;緊急迴避制御&quot; skill就可以連按兩次Boost掣使出急迴<br />\n (Default setting 即係連按X)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q:部機lv1用唔用到lv5武器？</strong><br />\nA:無限場所有lv都得 <br />\n限cost場要跟機lv, 高過部機過就降到你所持有嘅武器當中與機體同級或以下lv<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣出反格</strong><br />\nA. 對方出格鬥時按三角撞埋去, 判定時機請自行練習<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 格鬥點出二連斬三連斬</strong><br />\nA. 機體要有&quot;格鬥連擊制御&quot; Skill, lv1可以2hit, lv2可以3hit<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點解有人可以斬完又斬好似無硬直?</strong><br />\nA. 運用Boost Cancel 技巧就可以解除攻擊後嘅硬直(包括火箭炮, 加農炮, 格鬥, etc), 方法係攻擊後立即輕按Boost step 走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手製SETTING建議<br />\n打之前改改手製個SETTING<br />\nDefault 用X加速搞到加速其間好難轉方向<br />\nR1轉武R2射又令人好易轉錯武<br />\n所以改成<br />\nR1射<br />\nR2轉武<br />\nL1加速<br />\nX跳<br />\n其他不變<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 浴缸裡的貓, One.For.All, 高熱火焰, 闇之大精靈<br />\n<br />\n怎麼才算好泛機隊友? #曲<br />\n1.) 開場時散開衝, 唔好係我前面阻住我衝<br />\n2.) 到主戰場企係我前面擋彈, 等我定好位先好走<br />\n3.) 我射時唔該有後眼自動遠離我射線<br />\n4.) 我比人射時唔該有NT感應BOOST過黎幫我擋彈<br />\n5.) 擋完彈之後好馬上急回彈開等我可以零秒反擊<br />\n6.) 有格機打我你地要血肉長城保護我<br />\n7.) 就算因為保護我而死, 唔該死遠D兔得爆炸D光影響我, D煙唔該飄遠D唔好影響我開鏡"},{"pid":"1f8af863541c5f46013aa42208b1120138803440","tid":902793,"uid":137921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"希望新post新希望唔洗再做非洲之星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b261245bef82954ef7d12030c54241da0874f8b","tid":902793,"uid":5494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"成個星期冇開隻game"},{"pid":"8c4c282bb6b3688931732d671b3d53570a8ccbf3","tid":902793,"uid":43750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b261245bef82954ef7d12030c54241da0874f8b","tid":902793,"uid":5494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"成個星期冇開隻game"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"SAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2dcfdaa8ddd92a07d7cf24393491b49a0678b","tid":902793,"uid":91713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4c282bb6b3688931732d671b3d53570a8ccbf3","tid":902793,"uid":43750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b261245bef82954ef7d12030c54241da0874f8b","tid":902793,"uid":5494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"成個星期冇開隻game"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"SAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"我2個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新兵果10幾石仲未拎晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130dad6c5c363f033c